# Vite

> Next-generation frontend build tool with instant server start and lightning-fast HMR.

---

## Overview

Vite (French for "fast") is a modern build tool that provides:
- **Instant Dev Server**: No bundling during development
- **Lightning HMR**: Hot Module Replacement in milliseconds
- **Optimized Builds**: Rollup-based production builds
- **Framework Agnostic**: React, Vue, Svelte, and more
- **Native ESM**: Leverages browser ES modules

---

## Why Vite

| vs Webpack | vs Create React App |
|------------|---------------------|
| 10-100x faster dev start | No eject needed |
| Native ESM (no bundling) | Active maintenance |
| Simpler configuration | Modern defaults |
| Built-in TypeScript | Better DX |

### Performance Comparison

| Tool | Dev Server Start | HMR |
|------|------------------|-----|
| Vite | ~300ms | ~50ms |
| CRA/Webpack | 30-60s | 1-3s |

