## Quick Start

### Create New Project

```bash
# npm
npm create vite@latest my-app -- --template react-ts

# pnpm
pnpm create vite my-app --template react-ts

# Templates: vanilla, vanilla-ts, vue, vue-ts, react, react-ts,
# react-swc, react-swc-ts, preact, preact-ts, lit, lit-ts,
# svelte, svelte-ts, solid, solid-ts, qwik, qwik-ts
```

### Project Structure

```
my-app/
├── public/
│   └── favicon.ico
├── src/
│   ├── assets/
│   ├── components/
│   ├── App.tsx
│   ├── main.tsx
│   └── vite-env.d.ts
├── index.html          # Entry point (in root, not public)
