## Static Assets

### Import Assets

```typescript
// URL import
import imgUrl from "./img.png";
// imgUrl = "/assets/img.2d8e...png" (in production)

// Raw import (as string)
import shaderCode from "./shader.glsl?raw";

// Web Worker
import Worker from "./worker.ts?worker";
const worker = new Worker();

// Inline as base64
import inlineImg from "./img.png?inline";
```

### Public Directory

```
public/
├── favicon.ico      → /favicon.ico
├── robots.txt       → /robots.txt
└── images/
    └── logo.png     → /images/logo.png
```

Files in `public/` are served at root and not processed by Vite.

