## Build Optimization

### Code Splitting

```typescript
// Automatic with dynamic imports
const LazyComponent = lazy(() => import("./LazyComponent"));

// Manual chunks in config
build: {
  rollupOptions: {
    output: {
      manualChunks: {
        // Group vendor libraries
        vendor: ["react", "react-dom", "react-router-dom"],
        // Group UI libraries
        ui: ["@radix-ui/react-dialog", "@radix-ui/react-dropdown-menu"],
      },
      // Or use function
      manualChunks(id) {
        if (id.includes("node_modules")) {
          return "vendor";
        }
      },
    },
  },
},
```

### Tree Shaking

```typescript
// Use named imports for tree shaking
import { format } from "date-fns"; // Good - only imports format

import * as dateFns from "date-fns"; // Bad - imports everything
```

### Bundle Analysis

```bash
# Build with stats
npx vite build

# Analyze with visualizer plugin
# Or use external tools
npx source-map-explorer dist/assets/*.js
```

